---
import Slide from "../components/slide.astro";
---

<Slide>
	<h2>Plan for v3 release</h2>
	<p><strong>Phase 1:</strong> Site Builder (currently here)</p>
	<p><strong>Phase 2:</strong> Custom apps</p>
	<p><strong>Phase 3:</strong> Beta testing</p>
	<p><strong>Phase 4:</strong> Release candidate testing</p>
</Slide>

<Slide>
	<h3>Phase 1: Site Builder</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Browser support policy</li>
		<li>Design tokens</li>
		<li>Color theme</li>
		<li>Website components</li>
	</ul>
</Slide>

<Slide>
	<h3>Phase 2: Custom apps</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Form and JavaScript components</li>
		<li>Utility styles</li>
		<li>Stabilize HTML/CSS/JS APIs</li>
	</ul>
</Slide>

<Slide>
	<h3>Phase 3: Beta testing</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Quality assurance tooling</li>
		<li>Migration strategies</li>
		<li>Documentation</li>
		<li>Resources for designers (Figma)</li>
	</ul>
</Slide>

<Slide>
	<h3>Phase 4: Release candidate testing</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Bug squashing</li>
		<li>Ideally no more breaking API changes</li>
		<li>Clarify and expand documentation</li>
	</ul>
</Slide>

<Slide>
	<h3>Lifecycle (in months)</h3>
	<table>
		<thead>
			<tr>
				<th>Version</th>
				<th class="rvt-text-right">Development</th>
				<th class="rvt-text-right">Release</th>
			</tr>
		</thead>
		<tr>
			<th>v1</th>
			<td class="rvt-text-right">8</td>
			<td class="rvt-text-right">68</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<th>v2</th>
			<td class="rvt-text-right">32<b>*</b></td>
			<td class="rvt-text-right">44+</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<th>v3</th>
			<td class="rvt-text-right">10+</td>
			<td class="rvt-text-right">&mdash;</td>
		</tr>
	</table>
	<p><small><b>*</b> Priority changes during the pandemic paused development by 16 months.</small></p>
</Slide>

<Slide>
	<h3>Expected timetable</h3>
	<p><strong>Spring 2027:</strong> v3 release</p>
	<p><strong>Spring 2028:</strong> v2 end of life</p>
</Slide>
